---
globs: backend/test/**/*.spec.ts
alwaysApply: false
---

Strictly enforce the following testing architecture and conventions. No exceptions.

## 1. Directory & Naming (Strict Isolation)

- **Zero Tests in `src/`**: All test files must reside strictly within the `test/` directory.
- **Mirror `src/` Structure**: Under each test layer, replicate the `src/` subdirectory path. Map the source file path directly to the test path by swapping the layer prefix for `src/`.
  - `src/common/config/AplicationConfig.ts` -> `test/unit/common/config/AplicationConfig.spec.ts`
  - `src/lecture/lecture.service.ts` -> `test/integration/lecture/lecture.service.spec.ts`
- **Unified Suffix**: Always use `*.spec.ts`. Do NOT use `.unit.spec.ts` or `.int.spec.ts`.
- **Location-Based Type**: Testing layers are defined solely by their physical directory:
  - `test/unit/` -> Unit Tests (Domain, Entities, Pure functions)
  - `test/integration/` -> Integration Tests (Services, Modules, DB Container required)
  - `test/e2e/` -> E2E Tests (Endpoints, Guards, Playwright)

## 2. Test Layer Boundaries (Zero-Duplication)

- **Unit**: Strictly NO DB. Focus on pure business logic, algorithms, and state transitions. Minimize mocking.
- **Integration**: Requires local Docker DB. Validate all business scenarios, edge cases, and transaction failures at the Service layer (100% edge case coverage).
- **E2E**: Requires full app bootstrap + DB. Test Happy Path and Global Gatekeepers (JWT Guards, DTO Validations) only. Do not duplicate service edge cases.

## 3. Code Style & Conventions

- **Language**: All `describe` and `it` block text MUST be written in **Korean**.
- **AAA Pattern**: Explicitly structure every test case with `// given`, `// when`, and `// then` comments.
- **Sanitization**: Always call `vi.clearAllMocks();` inside the `afterEach` hook to prevent test pollution.

## 4. Blueprint Template

```typescript
describe("TargetClass", () => {
  afterEach(() => {
    vi.clearAllMocks();
  });

  describe("methodName", () => {
    it("조건에 맞는 명확한 한글 설명 기재", () => {
      // given
      const sampleData = { id: 1 };

      // when
      const result = TargetClass.methodName(sampleData);

      // then
      expect(result).toBeDefined();
    });
  });
});
```
